{"word":"rangers","count":1},{"word":"ready","count":1},{"word":"await","count":1},{"word":"orders","count":1},{"word":"yes","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"General!","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"We've got all equipment repaired, Tacetite weapons adjusted and given to Resonators. Non-Resonators are also equipped and prepared for action.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"But... the rain's getting heavier. Should we take shelter for the time being?","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"One of our combat medics claims it's no ordinary downpour, and he strongly advises holding off any moves until it clears.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Though young, his sharp intuition has been proven in previous battles. You've seen it firsthand.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"However... I do agree this will be our last chance at organizing another attack.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Sir, his name is...","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Ji...yan...","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"General, help... Please... help me...","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"General!","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"General... You look pale.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"We just detected an intense frequency reaction from that Tacet Field ahead.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"That moon... It's gradually turning full now, as you predicted.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"The sky... It looks just like how it was during the Battle Beneath the Crescent...","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Sir, the Midnight Rangers are ready. We await your orders.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Yes, sir!","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004}]}